OL,3,CTeenagers to be offered military gap
OL,4,Cyears to boost UK's defence
OL,6,FIt would be available to under-25s and
OL,7,Frecruits would not be deployed on
OL,8,Factive operations. It is not yet clear
OL,9,Fhow much they will be paid.
OL,11,FThe move comes after the Chief of the
OL,12,FDefence Staff, Air Chief Marshal Sir
OL,13,FRich Knighton, said Britain's "sons
OL,14,Fand daughters" should be "ready to
OL,15,Ffight" and called for a "whole of
OL,16,Fsociety" effort to defend the country
OL,17,Fin the face of Russian aggression.
