OL,3,CTeenagers to be offered military gap
OL,4,Cyears to boost UK's defence
OL,6,FDefence Secretary John Healey told the
OL,7,Fi paper the scheme would "give
OL,8,FBritain's young people a taste of the
OL,9,Fincredible skills and training on
OL,10,Foffer across the Army, Royal Navy and
OL,11,FRAF".
OL,13,FHe added: "As families come together
OL,14,Fat this time of year, and young people
OL,15,Fthink about their futures, I want the
OL,16,Foutstanding opportunities on offer in
OL,17,Four armed forces to be part of that
OL,18,Fconversation in homes across the UK."
