OL,3,CTeenagers to be offered military gap
OL,4,Cyears to boost UK's defence
OL,6,FThe Army scheme would see recruits
OL,7,Freceive 13 weeks of basic training as
OL,8,Fpart of a two-year placement, while
OL,9,Fthe Navy scheme would last one year
OL,10,Fand provide "profession agnostic"
OL,11,Ftraining for sailors, according to
OL,12,Freports.
OL,14,FThe RAF scheme is less developed, with
OL,15,Fthe branch said to be "scoping"
OL,16,Foptions.
OL,18,FThe Army currently offers gap year
OL,19,Fplacements for young people before,
OL,20,Fduring or immediately after
OL,21,Funiversity, which last one year.
