OL,3,CTeenagers to be offered military gap
OL,4,Cyears to boost UK's defence
OL,6,FSome 30 places are available on the
OL,7,FArmy internship scheme, formerly known
OL,8,Fas gap year commissions, but fewer
OL,9,Fthan 10 people were enrolled in 2024/
OL,10,F25.
OL,12,FThe internship is also only available
OL,13,Ffor those considering officer
OL,14,Ftraining, while the new gap year
OL,15,Fscheme is expected to be open more
OL,16,Fwidely.
