OL,3,CTeenagers to be offered military gap
OL,4,Cyears to boost UK's defence
OL,6,FAustralia already offers a gap year
OL,7,Fscheme for its military for those aged
OL,8,Fbetween 17 and 24.
OL,10,FIn 2023, 664 people enlisted in the
OL,11,FAustralian scheme, with a little more
OL,12,Fthan half going on to a permanent role
OL,13,Fin the country's defence force.
OL,15,FOther European countries have looked
OL,16,Fto national service in response to the
OL,17,Fthreat from Russia, with France,
OL,18,FGermany and Belgium introducing
OL,19,Fschemes this year.
